OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781867965
OL,3,CBritish man who killed terminally ill
OL,4,Cwife in Cyprus dies
OL,6,FA former miner from Northumberland who
OL,7,Fkilled his terminally ill wife in
OL,8,FCyprus has died.
OL,10,FDavid Hunter from Ashington spent 19
OL,11,Fmonths in jail after suffocating his
OL,12,Fwife Janice who had blood cancer in
OL,13,FDecember 2021.
OL,15,FHe said he had wanted to end her
OL,16,Fsuffering and had also tried to take
OL,17,Fhis own life at their home in Paphos.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/2
