PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781867965
OL,3,CBritish man who killed terminally ill
OL,4,Cwife in Cyprus dies
OL,6,FHunter had been on trial for murder
OL,7,Fbut in July 2023 judges ruled he was
OL,8,Fguilty of the lesser charge of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter and he was released from
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FHe stayed in Cyprus and said he wanted
OL,13,Fto be on the island with his wife who
OL,14,Fis buried there.
OL,16,FIn Northumberland former colleagues of
OL,17,FMr Hunter fundraised to pay for his
OL,18,Flegal fees and visited him in prison
OL,19,Fin Cyprus.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/2
